            2004,
            1014
          ],
          "block_id": 2,
          "block_order": 2
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "如：He is very poor cand he has litte money.(他很穷，几乎没有什么钱.))\nDon't worry,There is sti a litle time let.(别着急，还有一点时间呢)\nIn that polar region there live few people.(在那个极地地区几乎不住人。)\nYou can get a few sweets from him.(你可以从他那儿弄到一些糖果)\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            164,
            1034,
            1565,
            1834
          ],
          "block_id": 3,
          "block_order": 3
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "19)复合不定代词.somebody.somethin、anything.nothing.everything.everybody等是由some、any、no、every，加上body，thing构成的，叫做复合不定代词，在句子中当单数使用。somebody，something，someone般用于肯定句中；anything，anybody，anyone一般用于疑问句，否定句和条件状语从句中。修饰复合不定代词的定语，应放在它们的后面。如：Hey，Lily.There is someone ouside the door.，丽Did you meet anyone when you came to school last Sunday?(上个星期天你来学校时见到什么人3吗？)\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            69,
